### ── CATEGORIES ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create category
POST http://localhost:3001/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "RPG" }

###
### Create another category
POST http://localhost:3001/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Action" }

###
### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3001/categories

###
### Get category by id (replace with real id)
GET http://localhost:3001/categories/000000000000000000000001

###
### Update category
PUT http://localhost:3001/categories/000000000000000000000001
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "RPG & Strategy" }

###
### Delete category
DELETE http://localhost:3001/categories/000000000000000000000001

### ── PRODUCTS ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create product (without category)
POST http://localhost:3001/products
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Elden Ring", "about": "Souls-like épique", "price": 49.99, "categoryIds": [] }

###
### Create product with categories (replace IDs)
POST http://localhost:3001/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "The Witcher 3",
  "about": "RPG médiéval fantastique",
  "price": 19.99,
  "categoryIds": ["CATEGORY_ID_HERE"]
}

###
### Get all products (with categories joined)
GET http://localhost:3001/products

###
### Get product by id (replace with real id)
GET http://localhost:3001/products/000000000000000000000001

###
### Update product (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/products/000000000000000000000001
Content-Type: application/json

{ "price": 39.99 }

###
### Replace product (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:3001/products/000000000000000000000001
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Elden Ring DLC", "about": "Extension du jeu", "price": 24.99, "categoryIds": [] }

###
### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:3001/products/000000000000000000000001

###
### Validation error
POST http://localhost:3001/products
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "No Price" }
